    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>耶路撒冷之下</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一人称地下城探索：</strong>探索一个基于现实世界遗迹与圣城之下隐藏密道的幽闭、氛围浓郁的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/94c7a1d1863194637de391091b6d6af3.poster.avif?t=1771245099\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/94c7a1d1863194637de391091b6d6af3.webm?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/94c7a1d1863194637de391091b6d6af3.mp4?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>危机四伏的地牢</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鎏金亡者：</strong>面对“鎏金亡者”——那些被自身执念吞噬的前代探险者。他们为黄金进入这些隧道却再未离开；如今，他们如空洞躯壳般在黑暗中游荡，守护着他们的宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/f013b2f828849126d8ced26cc7eb1711.poster.avif?t=1771245099\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/f013b2f828849126d8ced26cc7eb1711.webm?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/f013b2f828849126d8ced26cc7eb1711.mp4?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>搜刮战利品并生存下去</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金是你唯一的筹码。你找到的每一枚硬币都必须带回地面，用以支付你的生存所需。<strong>明智管理你的资源</strong>，购买下次深入地下所需的装备和补给。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/c84ee2af42d98569e2d3b313a80330b2.poster.avif?t=1771245099\" width=800 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/c84ee2af42d98569e2d3b313a80330b2.webm?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/c84ee2af42d98569e2d3b313a80330b2.mp4?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实历史：地牢百科</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松并探索《地牢百科》，这是一部由历史学教授彼得主持的综合性百科全书。每获得一项成就即可解锁专属视频，了解你所发现遗迹与文物背后的真实故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/1aab440a66ffc7b512ed53478d612089.poster.avif?t=1771245099\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/1aab440a66ffc7b512ed53478d612089.webm?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015600/extras/1aab440a66ffc7b512ed53478d612089.mp4?t=1771245099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
